              "domain": null,
              "role": null,
              "type": "Directive",
              "value": "x"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "value": ". Collocation conditions are formed from the equality of the spline derivatives and rhs of the ODE system in the middle points between nodes."
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "children": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "value": "Such method is classified to Lobbato IIIA family in ODE literature. Refer to  for the formula and some discussion."
